Description: One-line, natively editable APA-style Word (.docx) tables and
    Word/PowerPoint-editable figures (EMF / DrawingML) for outputs of the MIT
    'categorical' package. Licensed GPL-3 because it renders via flextable and
    devEMF/rvg (GPL); 'categorical' itself stays MIT.
